  - Markus (Student)
  - Note from the author
  loadChats:
  - "This site is using a package filter. You know what it does? Basically it will
    block a certain device by its IP if it doesn\u2019t fit predefined parameters."
  - For the sake of this game the package filter will block some of your strongest
    devices (that send the most requests). You can bypass the filter by having more
    devices instead of fewer ones, because the filter can only block a limited amount
    of devices.
  completeNames:
  - Markus (Student)
  - Markus (Student)
  - Markus (Student)
  completeChats:
  - "Hello Mister, I heard of your local success with DDoS - Fanny told me. She also
    told me she shouldn\u2019t actually tell me. Well\u2026 "
  - "I\u2019m a student from Leimig University and programmed a website with a well
    established method for blocking DDoS attacks and I need someone to test it and
    collect data. Would you mind trying to DDoS this website which I\u2019ve set
    up?"
  - "I programmed it so you can\u2019t destroy anything - it\u2019s just for testing
    purposes."
  nameLinkToNextLevel: Markus (Student)
  linkToNextLevel: LINK TO WEBSITE
